        "曠流始毖泉，湎塗猶跬跡。——谢灵运《种桑》"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "湎"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "part_of_speech": "adjective",
      "meaning": "水流的样子。",
      "examples": [
